| Файл | Growth owns / co-owns |
|------|------------------------|
| `knowledge-base/marketing-brief.md` | Позиционирование, ICP, messaging, GTM |
| `knowledge-base/growth-playbook.md` | AARRR, воронки, channel playbook |
