## Coordination matrix (Muster)

| Role | Growth needs | Growth delivers |
|------|--------------|-----------------|
| **PM** | MVP scope, prioritization | Positioning input → `product-brief`; growth tasks `T-0xx` с AC |
| **IT-Architect** | Analytics host, privacy, OSS vs paid | Event schema requirements → ADR / architecture note |
| **Developer** | Instrumentation, landing if scoped | `READY` tasks: PostHog events, UTM, server-side identify |
| **UI/UX** | Conversion on key screens | Hypotheses on onboarding/dashboard first-run |
| **QA** | — | Verify tracking AC when in scope |

**Parallel agents:** Growth + PM в одном спринте — разные файлы (`marketing-brief` vs queue AC); не дублировать `IN_PROGRESS` на один task ID.

**Handoff flow (growth):** CMO strategy → PM (`READY` instrumentation/content) → Architect (analytics ADR) → Developer implement → QA verify events → CMO reads funnel.

